      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura movimento su file                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       scr-mov-fil-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se inserimento non si esaminano le righe dele-  *
      *              * tate                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "I"
                     go to scr-mov-fil-200.
       scr-mov-fil-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura riga "last removed"                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "LR"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se fine : a trattamento righe "in vita"         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to scr-mov-fil-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se riga precedente non esistente : riciclo      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
           if        w-rig-num-prg (2)    =    zero
                     go to scr-mov-fil-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Delete [hua]                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   del-rec-hua-000      thru del-rec-hua-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a prossima "last removed"               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-100.
       scr-mov-fil-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione sort preliminare per la scrittura    *
      *              * dei records [hua] ordinati per data validita'   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           sort      srt                  on   ascending srt-key
                     input  procedure     is   stp-srt-inp-000
                                          thru stp-srt-inp-999
                     output procedure     is   scr-rec-hua-000
                                          thru scr-rec-hua-999        .
       scr-mov-fil-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bufferizzazione ultimo codice super-agente      *
      *              * trattato per aggiornamento anagrafica agente    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cod-age (1)    to   w-agg-rec-age-sup      .
       scr-mov-fil-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento record [age]                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   agg-rec-age-000      thru agg-rec-age-999        .
       scr-mov-fil-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura record [hua]                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       scr-rec-hua-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione progressivo                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-scr-rec-hua-prg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se modifica                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "M"
                     go to scr-rec-hua-200.
       scr-rec-hua-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Delete record file righe [hua]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   del-mov-fil-000      thru del-mov-fil-999        .
       scr-rec-hua-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale archivio sortato [srt]      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se At End : ad uscita                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           return    srt    at end
                            go to scr-rec-hua-900                     .
       scr-rec-hua-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento progressivo                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       100                  to   w-scr-rec-hua-prg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Da record di sort ad area 'w-rig'               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      srt-dat-rig          to   w-rig                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-rec-hua-000      thru cmp-rec-hua-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Put record                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PT"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "sir/agb/fls/ioc/obj/iofhua"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-hua                 .
       scr-rec-hua-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a lettura record di sort                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-rec-hua-200.
       scr-rec-hua-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-rec-hua-999.
       scr-rec-hua-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
